replies.body:
Yeah, game rotation should be exactly that, a rotation. Not play a single game mode twice, until the entire queue has been played once each.
Would give us URF more often (which 90% of people seem to want), and give everyone else access to the modes they like. Personally i dont like any other rotation except URF, and havent tried doom bots but want to. But im happy to have the other modes queue up each week if it means URF will be unlocked more than twice a year
{{sticker:zombie-brand-mindblown}}
